data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Cape Coral! Situated in a prime location with a brand-new roof, an all-tiled interior, and a fenced yard, this property offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for its lucky future homeowners. This property's location is a true gem. You'll find yourself just moments away from the vibrant and charming downtown Cape Coral. Explore a wide array of restaurants, shops, parks, and cultural events without the hassle of a long commute. The home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for family and guests. The spacious living areas are filled with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. You'll have plenty of room for relaxation. The generous fenced backyard is a true sanctuary, this spacious outdoor area is perfect for entertainment. Whether you're looking for your forever home or an investment property, this is an excellent opportunity. The location, combined with the property's features and condition, makes it an attractive option for those seeking a slice of paradise in Cape Coral.
